      "id": "PopularPost71007",
      "post_content": "@Layton:  \n[Honor of the Pure](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Honor of the Pure)? This is more like [Glorious Anthem](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Glorious Anthem) or it's timeshifted version [Gaea's Anthem](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Gaea's Anthem), as they, unlike Honor, don't have the color restriction. Nonetheless this card is obviously much better than those because of the cheaper mana cost, as long as you don't mind that little -1.",
